<body>
<h3><i>This delays the execution of a list of micro-behaviours.</i></h3>
<p><font size="2" color="gray">Begin micro-behaviour</font>
</p>
<p><b>DO-AFTER</b></p>
<font size="2" color="gray">Begin NetLogo code:</font>
<pre>substitute-text-area-for delay-duration 1                                           
substitute-text-area-for comment Notes                                               
do-after delay-duration 
  [add-behaviours 
       list-of-micro-behaviours "Delayed Behaviours" []]
;comment</pre>
<font size="2" color="gray">End NetLogo code</font>
