<p><a href="WHENEVER.html">WHENEVER</a> -- Adds and removes micro-behaviours 
every time conditions are true</p>
	

<h2>Variants</h2>
<p>You can edit the duration field to any positive number. You can add 
micro-behaviours to the list of behaviours.</p>
<h2>How this works</h2>
<p>This relies upon the Behaviour Composer 
<a target="_blank" href="http://resources.modelling4all.org/documents/programming-guide#toc0">scheduling extensions</a> to NetLogo to 
run the list of micro-behaviours after a delay.</p>
